name: "Tingly" limited edition art print
description:
Signed and numbered by the artist, limited edition of only 50.

This exclusive, classic, deluxe, custom, designer, luxury, prestige, quality, premium, select, gourmet, digital art print is just right for you, and just right for your budget.

Print measures 7"x7ish" on 110 lb. dead tree pulp slices.
Ships tenderly packed and probably scrawled on (the envelope, not the print), with FREE domestic* shipping via USPS.

Every order includes one-of-a-kind, hand-drawn stickers by Dub.

*Free shipping applies only to orders shipped to US addresses.  International orders pay additional shipping fee.

name: "Leroy the Angry Unicorn"
description:
His name is Leroy, and he is really. fucking. pissed.

2012 Dub Williams
Aerosol on 30" x 30" Canvas

To have this hanging in someone's home would really please the shit out of me, so $100 or best offer.  email dub@artchainsaw.com.  If I don't take a loss shipping to wherever you are, i'll probably say yes.

If you're in the LA area, also willing to deliver - email me (dub@artchainsaw.com) instead of continuing with the cart.

name: "Slap Happy"
description:
Slap Happy
by Dub Williams 2013

Multimedia on canvas

This bold canvas features hand stenciled Priority Mail 228 labels individually spray-painted and tagged and then wrapped around this 7/8" this, 12 x 12" canvas. Highly glossy finish gives it a shiny wet look.  Signed by the artist, ready to hang.

name: "Wu-Bat" Plaque
description:
"It's the ruckus Gotham deserves, and it's the ruckus Gotham needs right now!"

The Wu-Bat Signal!
by Dub Williams 2013

These Wu-Tang / Batman logo mashups are all hand-painted aerosol on wooden plaques.  Squares are 5" x 5", circles are 5" diameter, and the ovals are 5" x 7".   Ready to hang. Signed front and back by the artist and come shipped, of course, with a couple of original slaps.

*Purchase also enlists buyer as lifetime member of the Bat-Tang Clan, gaining all privileges and benefits thereof (including but not limited to: bragging rights, tagging rights, on-demand collaborations, 2 nights on Dub's couch even on short notice, and borrowing $$ for your tacos because you forgot to hit the ATM.

name: "Art Hummingbird & Palette Rose"
description:
"The Art Hummingbird and the Palette Rose"

Dub Williams 
2013 - Ink and Acrylic
Set of 2 Hand Painted 8"x10" Canvases. 

This playful set of hand painted canvases can be hung next to each together or separately on opposite sides of a room.  This is a limited edition numbered series of only four sets of hand painted multiples ever being made.
